{"tid":1532202,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手後獨遊","createTime":"2019-09-02T12:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T12:59:24.000Z","uid":75013,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c2320225c25b643db4ace0af9505b91fb0f6fe64","tid":1532202,"uid":75013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"聽朝 我就要飛啦<br />\n分手前 你話過有諗過去搵我<br />\n但我知依家根本冇呢個可能<br />\n呢幾日我係咁希望你會出現係我既行程當中<br />\n但我知係冇可能發生既<br />\n旅行入面一定有好多野想同你分享 但根本唔可以搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近你好少po story 我好想知你既日常生活 好想知你過成點<br />\n但依家我連知道你幾時放假既資格都冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係可以每日望住你既在線上 我乜都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好想係黎緊幾日 可以係異地見你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36a69191e4fb35c02e6b856abc29d73ce0b4c31","tid":1532202,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:51:14.000Z","msg":"算啦巴打 你已經比我好 我直頭比人del contact <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3802fa9be7eb33c87af8470c5a2ae81fcfa4b1","tid":1532202,"uid":219216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4282ec134d314b97f8472a45e423125faa5fc543","tid":1532202,"uid":315924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:53:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫推到江永祥仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n仲有幾個鐘就返學啦好緊張<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529552</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bbf4af2d9645e2eed00b9aa6641c1df658718a1e","tid":1532202,"uid":118945,"like":0,"dislike":0,